      "rationale": "Testing was conducted exclusively under the nominal ASTM F1717 protocol at a single crosshead displacement rate and a single rod-to-screw fixation torque. Gradation 3 requires parametric variation of test conditions, which was not performed. This factor is below the required level and represents a known limitation of the validation dataset."
